Create a class named Student with the following specifications:

Attributes:
$name
$grades (an array of numeric values)

Methods:
__construct($name, $grades) - Initialize the attributes.
averageGrade() - Calculate and return the average of the grades.
displayResult() - Print a message displaying the student's name and their average grade.

 
<?php

